%%{init: {'theme': 'dark', 'themeVariables': {'primaryColor': '#1a56db', 'primaryTextColor': '#fff', 'lineColor': '#6b7280'}}}%%

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Analyst as Supply Chain Analyst
    participant Agent as SupplyShield Orchestrator
    participant DSA as detect_shipment_anomalies
    participant NSQ as news_scout_query (MCP)
    participant Scout as News Scout MCP Server
    participant ARI as assess_revenue_impact
    participant FAS as find_alternative_suppliers
    participant WF as supply_chain_recovery
    participant ES as Elasticsearch Serverless

    Analyst->>Agent: Shenzhen port congestion - any affected shipments?

    Note over Agent: Step 1 - DETECT
    Agent->>DSA: Call(delay_threshold=24)
    DSA->>ES: FROM sc_shipments WHERE delay_hours > 24 LOOKUP JOIN sc_suppliers LOOKUP JOIN sc_products
    ES-->>DSA: 14 rows (SUP-SZ-001, SUP-SZ-002, SUP-SZ-003)
    DSA-->>Agent: 14 delayed shipments, avg 143h delay

    Note over Agent: Step 2 - CORROBORATE via MCP
    Agent->>NSQ: Call(query="Shenzhen port congestion 2026")
    NSQ->>Scout: MCP request over HTTPS (ngrok tunnel)
    Scout->>ES: Hybrid search on sc_news (keyword + kNN)
    ES-->>Scout: 3 articles, severity=high, sentiment=-0.76
    Scout-->>NSQ: CONFIRMED signal, port backlog 8-10 days
    NSQ-->>Agent: CONFIRMED - 3 high-severity articles corroborate disruption

    Agent-->>Analyst: 14 shipments delayed, 3 Shenzhen suppliers. News Scout CONFIRMED - 3 articles, avg sentiment -0.77. Assess revenue?

    Analyst->>Agent: Yes - focus on Shenzhen Microtech first

    Note over Agent: Step 3 - ASSESS
    Agent->>ARI: Call(affected_supplier_id="SUP-SZ-001")
    ARI->>ES: FROM sc_orders LOOKUP JOIN sc_products WHERE primary_supplier_id == SUP-SZ-001 LOOKUP JOIN sc_suppliers
    ES-->>ARI: revenue_at_risk=$4.2M, orders=31, customers=8
    ARI-->>Agent: $4.2M at risk, 31 orders, 8 customers, due in 8 days

    Agent-->>Analyst: $4.2M revenue at risk. 31 orders, 8 customers, earliest due Feb 27. Find alternatives?

    Analyst->>Agent: Yes - microcontrollers, avoid East Asia

    Note over Agent: Step 4 - SOURCE ALTERNATIVES
    Agent->>FAS: Call(capability="microcontrollers", exclude_region="East Asia")
    FAS->>ES: FROM sc_suppliers EVAL suitability_score SORT DESC
    ES-->>FAS: 5 ranked alternatives
    FAS-->>Agent: Top: Viet Components (score 84.2, 18d, +10%), Penang TechFab (81.5, 21d, +12%)

    Agent-->>Analyst: Viet Components Vietnam score 84.2, 18-day lead, +10% cost. Penang TechFab Malaysia 81.5, 21 days, +12%. Create PO?

    Analyst->>Agent: Yes - 200 units SmartWatch Pro components

    Note over Agent: Step 5 - ACT (after confirmation)
    Agent->>WF: Trigger supply_chain_recovery(supplier=SUP-VIET-001, qty=200)
    WF->>ES: Index doc to sc_purchase_orders (PO-2026-0042)
    WF->>ES: Index doc to sc_actions_log (action=recovery_po_created)
    WF-->>Agent: PO-2026-0042 created, action logged

    Agent-->>Analyst: Done. PO-2026-0042 created with Viet Components for 200 units SmartWatch Pro. Action logged to audit trail. Total time: ~3 minutes.
